# Skills Directory: Reusable Workflows Only

Only put reusable, maintainable skill definitions under **.agents/skills/**.

- Add: Well-structured SKILL.md or .md files that define repeatable workflows (feature, debug, review, test, new-model, etc.)
- Do not add: One-off scripts, temporary debug helpers, or experiment-specific files.

Put temporary or one-off scripts in `scripts/`, `tests/`, or task-specific directories -- not in skills.
